**Algorithm:**
step-1: make 2 pointers d1 & d2 which will be pointing to L1 and L2 repectively.
step-2: keep iterating both the pointers (until both becomes NULL) by one step and assign to one- other linked-list if any of the pointer reaches NULL.
sep-3: If there is a intersection point then definitely d1 == d2 at some point then we will return either d1 or d2.


